title: Full Stack Software Developer Jumps Out of Ground Story Window
body:
Seattle, Thursday

Student software dev Mickey Cowan dove out of his basement window in an attempt to "stop thinking about the broken view" in one of his homework assignments. Prior to this radical and colossal failure to end his temporary frustration, Cowan was overheard saying, "Well the goddamn CHOCOLATE didn't help, so maybe THIS'LL work!" Paramedics were not called to the scene and no one actually saw Cowan get up, brush himself off, and return to his keyboard.
name: Full Stack Software Developer Jumps Out of Ground Story Window

title: Project Four Is Looming
body: Along with the inevitability of Climate Change and the extinction of humanity hinging on the way in which international bodies will address it, Project Four for GA Seattle's WDI-23, is looming. For some, like Carlo, this is just another day at the office. But for several of the intrepid cohort, fear and loathing is operating at full throttle.
